mx-installer (0.2.3) unstable; urgency=low 
   
  * installer adds boot parameters.
  * changed code for replacing sting in /etc/default/grub.
  * replaced single quotes with double in sed.
  * disable automount in Thunar.
  * services screen is hidden and called by 'Advanced' button.
  * modified location view Services button.
  * changed translation location to match other mx tools.
  * changed MX-14 to MX Linux and other strings.
  * changed minstall_ to mx-installer_ in app.cpp.
  * added .qm files and added Japanes in src.pro.

